Myrmidon is silent for a long thoughtful moment,
Hydras' words 'old team destroyed' echoing loudly
through Myrmidon's head. It was not fear for himself
that motivated Myrmidon's silence, but disquiet of a
completely different sort. "It is a rare leader that
survives the destruction of his entire force." 

Myrmidon turned back to Hydras, his optics unreadable,
"What happened? And tell me of this Prime, is he a
worthy adversary?"

Preston
(Myrmidon)
